   Marginal Models for Longitudinal Proportional Data. \emph{ Biometrical Journal,} 
   \bold{ 46:} 540--553
   
   Qiu Z. (2001) \emph{ Simplex Mixed Models for Longitudinal Proportional Data.} 
   Ph.D. Dissertation, York University
